config MUIC_HV_FORCE_LIMIT
        bool "Force limit AFC QC MAX CHG VOLTAGE"
        depends on HV_MUIC_MAX77843_AFC
        default n
        help
          If you say yes here you will add function of limit afc charging volatage.
